@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hrzeug(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.sin(v0)
    v1 = (v2 - 0.55)
    tmp = (v2 / 0.47)
    tmp = (wp.sin(0.42) / wp.abs(wp.cos(v1 + 0.67)))
    v2 = ((wp.sin(v2 + 0.45) - wp.abs(v0 + 0.28)) / wp.exp(v0))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.sin(wp.abs(tmp + 0.61)))
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.sin(0.93))
    data[tid] = v0
